    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a functional daily driver. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though the exterior shows its age with several noticeable paint chips, some fading on the hood, and a minor scuff on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows typical wear and tear from consistent use. It's a solid, honest car that is ready for the road, provided you don't mind a bit of character in its appearance.",
