    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained over the years. The engine and transmission operate smoothly, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience. All major mechanical systems are in solid working order, and the interior has been kept clean with only minor signs of regular use. While the exterior may show a few small cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and structurally sound. It is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality vehicle that is ready for the road.",
